---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { profile } from "../data/profile";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About | Shiqing Gao"
  description="About Shiqing Gao, a mathematics undergraduate interested in applied mathematics, computational imaging, writing, and project-based learning."
>
  <header class="container page-header personal-header">
    <p class="eyebrow">About / 关于我</p>
    <h1>在数学之外，也在具体的项目里认识问题。</h1>
    <p class="english-lead">{profile.englishSummary}</p>
  </header>

  <section class="container about-intro section">
    <div class="about-label">A little context</div>
    <div class="prose bilingual-prose">
      <p>{profile.bio}</p>
      <p>我喜欢通过项目学习：先做出一个最小可运行版本，再逐步加入实验、指标、可视化和文字总结。这个网站也是这个过程的一部分，它让我认真考虑什么值得展示、怎样表达才算清楚，以及下一步应该往哪里走。</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-band">
    <div class="container about-grid">
      <article class="about-section">
        <span>01</span>
        <h2>Currently / 最近</h2>
        <p>正在继续整理图像反问题实验，完善个人网站，并把零散的项目过程写成更容易复盘的记录。</p>
      </article>
      <article class="about-section">
        <span>02</span>
        <h2>What I’m exploring / 我在探索</h2>
        <p>{profile.interests.join(" · ")}</p>
      </article>
      <article class="about-section">
        <span>03</span>
        <h2>How I learn / 学习方式</h2>
        <p>Build a small version, test it, look for failure cases, and write down what changed. 我更喜欢用可以运行、比较和解释的东西来检验理解。</p>
      </article>
      <article class="about-section">
        <span>04</span>
        <h2>Beyond coursework / 课程之外</h2>
        <p>我也关心写作、语言、设计、音乐、社团和游戏。这些兴趣不一定都需要变成“成果”，但会影响我观察和表达问题的方式。</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
